{"id":616524,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/08/【盛世一景】赤纳粹旗（chinazi-flag）/","date":"2019-08-31T17:21:19Z","modified":"2019-08-31T17:21:19Z","title":"【盛世一景】赤纳粹旗（ChiNazi flag）","content":"<p>8月31日，香港抗议者在街头打出纳粹版“中华人民共和国国旗”，称之为“赤纳粹旗（CHINAZI旗）”。#Chinazi目前已经在推特上形成了一个较为广传的<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Chinazi?src=hashtag_click\">tag</a>，使用者多认为中共统治下的极权国家是“21世纪的纳粹”。</p>\n<blockquote><p>过去一个月，「#Chinazi」这个结合「China」与「Nazi」的新词正在网路社群媒体中蔓延。「Chinazi」这个词不但将中共政权的统治手法与纳粹德国相提并论，更有论者认为，倘若「反送中」抗争失败，则香港将成为「新疆2.0」，西元2047年后将再也没有「香港人」。  —— <a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2896693\">自由时报</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/600_phpxynfsT.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-616528\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/600_phpxynfsT.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"595\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/600_phpxynfsT.jpg 726w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/600_phpxynfsT-227x300.jpg 227w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EDSoP7dVUAEk30A.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-616527\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EDSoP7dVUAEk30A.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"304\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EDSoP7dVUAEk30A.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EDSoP7dVUAEk30A-300x166.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EDSWd7ZU4AAQlk8.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-616526\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EDSWd7ZU4AAQlk8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EDSWd7ZU4AAQlk8.png 660w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EDSWd7ZU4AAQlk8-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EDSRchCVAAMiWv9.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-616529\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EDSRchCVAAMiWv9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EDSRchCVAAMiWv9.jpg 680w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EDSRchCVAAMiWv9-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">China is the new Nazi Party, this group of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HongKongProtestors?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HongKongProtestors</a> say <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/chinazi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#chinazi</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/antiELAB?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#antiELAB</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/aVBmkxnhj1\">pic.twitter.com/aVBmkxnhj1</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Victor Ting (@VictorTing7) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/VictorTing7/status/1167715426136207361?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 31, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Spread it out<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/chinazi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#chinazi</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/NSisNBiXiS\">pic.twitter.com/NSisNBiXiS</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; slnw_216 (@216Slnw) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/216Slnw/status/1167126564049260544?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 29, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-wid